title: Un Koreano está haciendo destrozos con Rumble!

embed.description: League of Legends (LOL) Season 6 Patch 6.18. Video on the Diamond 2 Korean player with a 100% win rate on Rumble and is also the highest rated/ranked lolskill player on a single champ on lolskill's website. In this video I just go over how he managed the 56 game winning streak and quickly go through his standard item build.
